title: Shaniqua Edwards is ready to win
text: Shaniqua Edwards is ready to win Mike Libert NYCHoops.net 6'2" forward Shaniqua Edwards (Grand Street Campus '17) has set her goals a bit higher this season, not content this time around in just getting there, but wanting to win the school's first ever girls basketball title. ...
